<item>
            <title>[AMQ-5182] ActiveMQ web demo - chat example - Very slow on JBoss7 after AMQ-4801</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-5182</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running the chat example on JBoss 7, the Ajax Servlet uses the Jetty Servlet 3.0 Continuation support.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The chat client is terribly slow in this case. A chat message is only received when the polling connector starts polling, every 30 seconds.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In ActiveMQ 5.8, the chat messages come in immediately.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;JBoss-AS 7.2.0&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12713666">AMQ-5182</key>
